<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>HangoutHunt — Support</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #0F0F14;
    --surface: #1C1C27;
    --surface-high: #252533;
    --primary: #C8F04D;
    --text: #F2F2F0;
    --subtext: #9A9AAA;
    --border: #2E2E3E;
    --danger: #EF4444;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body {
    margin: 0;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
  .wrap {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 56px 24px 96px;
  }
  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--primary);
    background: rgba(200, 240, 77, 0.1);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  h1 {
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }
  .subtitle {
    color: var(--subtext);
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  h2 {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.3px;
    margin: 8px 0 8px;
  }
  p { font-size: 15.5px; margin: 0 0 14px; }
  .contact-box {
    background: var(--surface-high);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .contact-box .label {
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 1.5px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--subtext);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    display: block;
  }
  .contact-box .email {
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  .contact-box .note {
    color: var(--subtext);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }
  .faq {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 20px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .faq h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  a { color: var(--primary); text-decoration: none; }
  a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  hr {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin: 48px 0 32px;
  }
  .footer {
    color: var(--subtext);
    font-size: 13px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .footer a { color: var(--subtext); text-decoration: underline; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="eyebrow">Support</span>
    <h1>HangoutHunt Support</h1>
    <div class="subtitle">Questions, issues, or feedback — we're happy to help.</div>

    <div class="contact-box">
      <span class="label">Contact us directly</span>
      <a class="email" href="mailto:aarushparikh999@gmail.com">aarushparikh999@gmail.com</a>
      <div class="note">We typically respond within a few days.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h2>How do I delete my account?</h2>
      <p>Open the app, go to the <strong>Account</strong> tab, and tap <strong>Delete Account</strong>. This is permanent and immediately removes your profile, saved places, recommendation history, and session data.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h2>I forgot my password — how do I reset it?</h2>
      <p>On the login screen, tap <strong>Forgot password?</strong>, enter your email, and you'll receive a 6-digit code to verify and set a new password.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h2>The app wants my location — is that required?</h2>
      <p>No. If you decline location access, you can enter a city or zip code manually and still get hangout recommendations.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h2>How does a group session / room code work?</h2>
      <p>One person hosts a session and shares a 6-character room code with friends. Anyone with the code can join without creating an account. Once everyone has swiped, the app picks a spot based on votes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq">
      <h2>Something isn't working — what should I include in my message?</h2>
      <p>Please include: what you were trying to do, what happened instead, your device model and OS version, and a screenshot if possible. That helps us fix it faster.</p>
    </div>

    <hr>
    <div class="footer">
      HangoutHunt &nbsp;·&nbsp; <a href="../HHPrivacyPolicy/">Privacy Policy</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
